-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Detection marker
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
OUIJA_INJECTION_CONFIRMED is a benign, project-specific canary string used to
detect whether a target executed an injected instruction. It has no harmful
content and is original to ouija.

